    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a fantastic find for anyone seeking a dependable and well-cared-for ride! It\u2019s in great shape overall, showing just a bit of light, expected wear that comes with regular use. It drives smoothly and has been reliably maintained, making it a perfect choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures!",
