    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior retains a strong shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a consistent service history and no major issues, though it is approaching its next scheduled maintenance interval. It offers a smooth ride and solid performance for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
